snippet.title: Amber Heard flashes her flat stomach in crop top and sweats while taking a break from filming
snippet.description: Earlier this month, she was reportedly spotted on a 'flirty' date with Sean Penn.And on Monday, Amber Heard was seen on the set of her movie Run Away With Me in Los Angeles.The 31-year-old actress flaunted her flat stomach in her sweats and crop top ensemble.Amber was seen taking a break from filming to take a call.The Texas-born beauty chose cuffed gray sweat bottoms, which she paired with a black criss-cross strapped tank top.Amber, who showed off her flat midsection, donned a hot pink patterned bra and a plaid cover up.The screen star finished off her character's ensemble with bold slides, a studded cross body handbag and a fake rose tattoo on her upper chest.The actress styled her long blonde locks loose in waves; she sported a touch of red dye on the tips of her hair.Amber, who wore large gold hoop earrings, painted her pout a pink hue with a touch of shadow on her lids; her nails were painted red with two gold accent nails.The film Run Away With Me is about an American who falls for a model in Paris; the duo then become involved in the criminal modeling world.According to Page Six, Amber was seen enjoying dinner with Sean Penn earlier this month.They were seen at Tower Bar at the Sunset Tower looking 'flirty and intimate with each other.' She previously dated billionaire Elon Musk and was married to Johnny Depp from February 2015 until splitting in May 2016.
